name: Open Source Projects at TUW-GEO
tagline: an overview of the open source projects of the Department of Geodesy and Geoinformatics of the Vienna University of Technology.
body:
* [pytesmo](http://github.com/TUW_GEO/pytesmo) - python Toolbox for the Evaluation of Soil Moisture Observations
* [OGRSpatialRef3D](https://github.com/ottointhesky/OGRSpatialRef3D) - Rigorous support of Vertical Datums within OGRSpatialReference
